  "purpose": "(Clinical Focus: All prescribable medication formulations represented using  a \"brand-specific\" concept developed to support HL7 C-CDA R2 October 2013 ballot.),(Data Element Scope: medication orderable),(Inclusion Criteria: Prescribable medications including multiple ingredient medications. Intersection (\nUnion(FilterOnProperty(TTY,SBDG), FilterOnProperty(TTY,SBDF), FilterOnProperty(TTY,SBD), FilterOnProperty(TTY,BPCK),\nFilterOnProperty(TTY,SBDC))),(Exclusion Criteria: Non-prescribable (OTC) drugs. Concepts representing \"generic\" (non-proprietary) concepts)",
